Winoci ICON WINOCI.ICO
ABOUTBOX DIALOG LOADONCALL MOVEABLE DISCARDABLE 9, 27, 140, 92
CAPTION "About Winoci"
STYLE WS_BORDER | WS_CAPTION | WS_DLGFRAME | WS_POPUP
BEGIN
